Entry.JapaneseText: 出せー、僕を ここから出せよー！
Entry.EnglishText: Lemme out! Lemme out I said!

Entry.JapaneseText: 虫じゃない！ 僕は妖精だ！
Entry.EnglishText: I'm not a bug dammit! I'm a fairy!

Entry.JapaneseText: ふん、 オレとおまえが同じ？ 違うね
Entry.EnglishText: You think you and I are the same? How wrong you are.

Entry.JapaneseText: おまえ、アルテミスだろ
だったら、 なんだってんだよ
やっぱりな。 <CLE>に聞いてたんだ
Entry.EnglishText: Knew it, I've heard from <CLE> about you.

Entry.JapaneseText: 口の悪い小生意気な妖精に 会ったってさ
Entry.EnglishText: He said he met such a foul mouthed fairy once.

Entry.JapaneseText: <CLE>なんてそんなやつ 知らないもんね
Entry.EnglishText: I don't know any dumb pricks named <CLE>.

Entry.JapaneseText: ねぇ？ どういうこと？ ぼく、妖精じゃないの？
Entry.EnglishText: Hey, what did you mean? I'm not a fairy?
Are you blind that you can't see the difference?

Entry.JapaneseText: キュートな羽根も すらりとした体も 全然違う。だろ？
Entry.EnglishText: From the cute feathers to the long and slender body, you got it all wrong.

Entry.JapaneseText: だとしたら、 きみが妖精じゃない、 とか……
Entry.EnglishText: If that's the case, you aren't a fairy either, really...

Entry.JapaneseText: なんでそうなるんだよ
そもそも、おまえこそ 勝手にそう思い込んでる だけじゃないのか？
Entry.EnglishText: To begin with are you really convinced to be a fairy this much?

Entry.JapaneseText: ぼくが……思い込んでた、 だけ……？
Entry.EnglishText: I'm...being convinced to be a fairy...?

Entry.JapaneseText: じゃあ、 ぼくは何なの？
Entry.EnglishText: In that case, what am I?

Entry.JapaneseText: ふん、 ここから出してくれたら、 教えてやってもいいけどね
Entry.EnglishText: Heh! If you want to know get me out of here first!

Entry.JapaneseText: うぉっ！ こりゃ、やばいな
Entry.EnglishText: Wow! That's some dangerous stuff here!

Entry.JapaneseText: 意地悪魔術師のじじぃに 呪文かけられたんだ！
Entry.EnglishText: It's a first-class level curse spell!

Entry.JapaneseText: こんなやつ ほっといていこーぜ
Entry.EnglishText: I say we leave him rotting here.

Entry.JapaneseText: でも、 エトのことが……
いーじゃん、別にエトが、 妖精と違くても、 何かが変わるわけでもなし
Entry.EnglishText: It's okay. Even if Eto isn't a fairy, it wouldn't really change a thing to know what she is.

Entry.JapaneseText: そうかな…… ……うん、そうかも……
Entry.EnglishText: Yeah...I guess you got a point...

Entry.JapaneseText: ま、そういうわけだ。 悪いな
あ、こら、待ってよ！ ヒドイぞ！
Entry.EnglishText: Hey wait right there! You jerks!

Entry.JapaneseText: マクスウェルに 頼んでみたらどうかな？
Entry.EnglishText: Couldn't we ask Maxwell to set you free?

Entry.JapaneseText: 待ってて。ぼくたちが 解放してあげるかラ
Entry.EnglishText: Please wait! We'll set you free!
